title: Levi's Women's 725 High Rise Bootcut Jeans (Also Available in Plus)
description: Designed to give you legs for days
Fits slim through your hip and thigh with a high rise that holds you in

The Levi's Womens 725 High Rise Bootcut boasts a classic silhouette with modern touches. The five-pocket jean features a modern high waist with a slim fit in the hip and thigh that flows to a generous knee break. Signature arcuate stitch accents the back pockets. Belt loop waistband with brand patch at the back waist, zipper fly, and button closure. 78% cotton, 21% polyester, 1% elastane. Machine wash.
